        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N314_VC_18_FR"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/42.001944444_9.050833333"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The MOVING reference member state of this VC (Value Chain) is FRANCE INRAE. The reference MOVING Card ID of this VC is VC 18 FR. The construction of the value of apples from the Prunelli region results from the revival of several small orchards, the voluntarism of the mayors of the localities and the commitment of the village community around the annual apple fair organized alternately in Todda and in Bastelica.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


